title: [Temple of Industry, Rock Garden]
description: High-walled stucco terraces shield the granite walk from the sun and salty wind.  Each plot boasts arrangements of stone and hardy plants.  Silvery cacti peek from the crags and nooks formed by intersecting stones, their occasional crimson-petaled flowers and blushed violet fruits breaking the monochrome.

High-walled stucco terraces shield the granite walk from the sharp-breathed night breeze.  Each plot boasts arrangements of stone and hardy plants.
